Technical information
===============================================================================

Important Giellatekno SVN addresses:

SME Monodix: https://victorio.uit.no/langtech/trunk/gt/sme

Bidix: https://victorio.uit.no/langtech/trunk/words/dicts

==Monodix==

SME:

* The monodix is a subset of the GT sme transducer. 
** The file apertium-sme-nob.sme.twol should be kept up to date with
   twol-sme.txt (or, `tmp/sme-twol.hfst.txt` as produced by
   `make GTLANG=sme hfst` in the giellatekno/trunk/gt folder)
** The file apertium-sme-nob.sme.lexc should be kept up to date using 
   the update-morph/update-lexc.py script

NOB: 

* The monodix should probably be kept up to date with the 
  one in apertium-sme-nob, however
* we allow some differences in closed category words. 

